1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:05,439
For a doctoral researcher, the challenge is not only coding the material.

2
00:00:05,439 --> 00:00:09,904
It is retaining enough context and methodological reasoning to explain

3
00:00:09,904 --> 00:00:14,369
the analysis months later to a supervisor, examiner or future

4
00:00:14,369 --> 00:00:14,816
reader.

5
00:00:15,216 --> 00:00:20,165
QualCanvas includes a public methodology field guide covering several approaches

6
00:00:20,165 --> 00:00:22,145
and ethics in practice.

7
00:00:22,145 --> 00:00:27,094
Use it as orientation, then follow the literature, supervision and

8
00:00:27,094 --> 00:00:29,568
protocol that govern your study.

9
00:00:29,968 --> 00:00:34,244
The canvas helps you keep excerpts, categories and memos connected

10
00:00:34,244 --> 00:00:35,955
while the study grows.

11
00:00:35,955 --> 00:00:40,231
Use separate canvases or clear groups for phases when one

12
00:00:40,231 --> 00:00:44,080
workspace becomes harder to explain than the research itself.

13
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:48,987
Write memos that capture the reason for changes in the

14
00:00:48,987 --> 00:00:51,691
codebook, sampling decisions and developing claims.

15
00:00:51,691 --> 00:00:56,648
These notes become valuable when drafting the methods and findings chapters.

16
00:00:57,048 --> 00:01:01,666
A supervisor can give better feedback when code names are

17
00:01:01,666 --> 00:01:03,975
supported by definitions and excerpts.

18
00:01:03,975 --> 00:01:08,593
Review the codebook together without treating code frequency as a

19
00:01:08,593 --> 00:01:10,440
substitute for analytical importance.

20
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:16,120
Use reports for drafting, Excel for structured review and canvas

21
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,232
images for explaining relationships.

22
00:01:18,232 --> 00:01:23,512
Remove or protect participant material before sharing any export outside

23
00:01:23,512 --> 00:01:25,624
the approved research environment.

24
00:01:26,024 --> 00:01:30,854
The most defensible dissertation describes the process that actually happened.

25
00:01:30,854 --> 00:01:35,684
Keep the method, evidence, decisions, revisions and claims connected from

26
00:01:35,684 --> 00:01:40,514
the beginning, and the final writing becomes more honest and

27
00:01:40,514 --> 00:01:41,480
more manageable.
